erif; letter-spacing: 0px;">on this page&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">where some discount codes can be found!</span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Separator" data-key="separator" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1684149359517" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1684149359517"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1684149359617" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1684149359617" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-md" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/54084887-56a7-45be-94e9-821bb67a2e1e/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/Love%20sory%202.png" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="35%" data-height="auto" title="" width="1220" height="343" natural-width="1220" natural-height="343"></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1684142683979" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1684142683979" data-layout-lg="8+4" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="8+4" data-layout-sm="8+4" data-layout-xs="12+12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-8 gf_col-md-8 gf_col-sm-8 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1684142666919" data-id="1684142666919"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1684143222410" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1684143222410"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 750px !important; height: 597.344px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 375px 298.672px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 750px !important; height: 597px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="81" height="38" style="display: none; top: 32px !important; left: 521px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-808012" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Meet Kenny and Britney, 2 single hotties who met through a special app called B-inder. Kenny lives in sunny paradise Malibu, while Britney lives on the other side of B-planet in a </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">snow white</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> charming little village called B-town. </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; text-align: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap;">Kenny and Britney texted and FaceTimed constantly. As they shared </span><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; text-align: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(216, 28, 28);"></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; text-align: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap;">everything with each other, something amazing happened—they fell madly in love! Their hearts felt warm and glowy whenever they talked, and they couldn't wait to meet in person.</span></p><p><b style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal;"><br></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">However, there was one big problem. The distance between Malibu and B-town was enormous! It takes </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">33</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> hours to fly from one place to the other. They couldn't just jump on a scooter or ride a magical unicorn to meet each other. </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; text-align: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap;">After six months of talking every day, Britney had an idea, she bravely asked Kenny if he wanted to move in together. It was not just a weekend getaway, it was a big decision and Kenny needed some time to think about it.</span></p><p><b style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal;"><br></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Weeks passed, and Britney anxiously waited for Kenny's answer. She wondered if he felt the same way about their love, and if they could find a way to be together. But no matter how much she checked her phone, no message from Kenny arrived. </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; text-align: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap;">Little did Britney know, Kenny was going through a remarkable transformation inside his heart. He realized that Britney was the one he wanted to be with forever. So, he decided to do something special to surprise her.</span></p><p><b style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal;"><br></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Kenny took a cute selfie while holding a </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">coconut</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> drink </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">on the beach and got it printed as a postcard. He grabbed a pen and wrote a romantic message to Britney. He told her how much he loved her and that he had booked a flight for her to come to Malibu. With excitement bubbling inside him, Kenny sent the postcard on its way. </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; text-align: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap;">Sadly, on its journey to B-town, the postcard encountered a little hiccup. There was a delivery issue, and poor Britney never received the card! She didn't know about Kenny's grand gesture and his plan to bring her to Malibu.</span></p><p><b style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal;"><br></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Can you help Britney to get to Kenny?!</span></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-4 gf_col-md-4 gf_col-sm-4 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1684142698380" data-id="1684142698380"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1684147236689" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1684147236689" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-sm" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/91880c93-fbb5-48ed-b189-9814b40a864c/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/Britney2.png" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" width="570" height="575" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="